{"input": "write me a poem about nothing at all", "context": {"userDetails": {"name": "Kim", "language": "en"}, "location": "Oslo", "timezone": "Europe/Oslo", "messages": [{"role": "system", "content": "Summary: User likes abstract concepts."}]}, "output": "Nothing sat quietly in the corner of everything,\nwearing a coat made of absence.\nIt hummed a tune with no melody\nand wrote its name in invisible ink.", "category": "edge"}